  fhir:DomainResource.text [
     fhir:Narrative.status [ fhir:value "generated" ] ;
     fhir:Narrative.div "<div xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\"><p class=\"res-header-id\"><b>Generated Narrative: ValueSet IMMZD18SDTPPregnancyStartingWith4DosesVS</b></p><a name=\"IMMZD18SDTPPregnancyStartingWith4DosesVS\"> </a><a name=\"hcIMMZD18SDTPPregnancyStartingWith4DosesVS\"> </a><p>This value set expansion contains 3 concepts.</p><table class=\"codes\"><tr><td><b>System</b></td><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\"><b>Code</b></td><td><b>Display</b></td><td><b>Definition</b></td></tr><tr><td><a name=\"IMMZD18SDTPPregnancyStartingWith4DosesVS-http://smart.who.int/immunizations/CodeSystem/IMMZDAK-The|20primary|20DTP|20series|20has|20been|20completed,|20first|20tetanus|20and|20diphtheria|20booster|20dose|20was|20administered|20and|20client|20is|20currently|20pregnant-276\"> </a><code>http://smart.who.int/immunizations/CodeSystem/IMMZDAK</code></td><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">  <a href=\"CodeSystem-IMMZDAK.html#IMMZDAK-TheprimaryDTPserieshasbeencompleted.44firsttetanusanddiphtheriaboosterdosewasadministeredandclientiscurrentlypregnant-276\">The primary DTP series has been completed, first tetanus and diphtheria booster dose was administered and client is currently pregnant-276</a></td><td>The primary DTP series has been completed, first tetanus and diphtheria booster dose was administered and client is currently pregnant</td><td><div><p>\"Completed the primary vaccination series\" = TRUE (where \"Vaccine type\" = \"DTP-containing vaccines\") AND Count of vaccines administered where \"Vaccine type\" = \"Tetanus and diphtheria-containing vaccines\" and \"Type of dose\" = \"Booster dose\") = 1 AND \"Currently pregnant\" = TRUE</p>\n</div></td></tr><tr><td><a name=\"IMMZD18SDTPPregnancyStartingWith4DosesVS-http://smart.who.int/immunizations/CodeSystem/IMMZDAK-Second|20tetanus|20and|20diphtheria|20booster|20dose|20was|20administered-140\"> </a><code>http://smart.who.int/immunizations/CodeSystem/IMMZDAK</code></td><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">  <a href=\"CodeSystem-IMMZDAK.html#IMMZDAK-Secondtetanusanddiphtheriaboosterdosewasadministered-140\">Second tetanus and diphtheria booster dose was administered-140</a></td><td>Second tetanus and diphtheria booster dose was administered</td><td><div><p>Count of vaccines administered (where \"Vaccine type\" = \"Tetanus and diphtheria-containing vaccines\" and \"Type of dose\" = \"Booster dose\") = 2</p>\n</div></td></tr><tr><td><a name=\"IMMZD18SDTPPregnancyStartingWith4DosesVS-http://smart.who.int/immunizations/CodeSystem/IMMZDAK-Third|20tetanus|20and|20diphtheria-containing|20booster|20dose|20was|20administered.|20Tetanus|20and|20diphtheria|20immunization|20schedule|20has|20been|20completed.-260\"> </a><code>http://smart.who.int/immunizations/CodeSystem/IMMZDAK</code></td><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">  <a href=\"CodeSystem-IMMZDAK.html#IMMZDAK-Thirdtetanusanddiphtheria-containingboosterdosewasadministered.46Tetanusanddiphtheriaimmunizationschedulehasbeencompleted.46-260\">Third tetanus and diphtheria-containing booster dose was administered. Tetanus and diphtheria immunization schedule has been completed.-260</a></td><td>Third tetanus and diphtheria-containing booster dose was administered. Tetanus and diphtheria immunization schedule has been completed.</td><td><div><p>Count of vaccines administered (where \"Vaccine type\" = \"Tetanus and diphtheria-containing vaccines\" and \"Type of dose\" = \"Booster dose\") = 3\n\"Immunization recommendation status\" = \"Complete\" (where \"Vaccine type\" = \"Tetanus and diphtheria-containing vaccines\")</p>\n</div></td></tr></table></div>"
